Entry.JapaneseText: あのオヤジは一体、何者なんだ!? 普通じゃなかったぞ！
Entry.EnglishText: What was up with that old man?! Something was wrong with him!

Entry.JapaneseText: でも、フォルスは感じなかったんだ。 考えられるとしたら……
Entry.EnglishText: I couldn't sense any Force. But come to think of it...

Entry.JapaneseText: ああっ、まさか、これって……!?

Entry.EnglishText: Do you know what's going on?!

Entry.JapaneseText: ひとつだけ!! でも、そうなの、<Eugene>!?
Entry.EnglishText: I can't think of anything else! What do you think, <Eugene>?!

Entry.JapaneseText: そう思いたくはないが……
Entry.EnglishText: It pains me to think it, but...

Entry.JapaneseText: とにかく、あのオヤジを捕まえて 確かめるしかない！
Entry.EnglishText: We'll know when we catch that old man!
